          "value": "<p>As a full action, a thermatrod can spray a portion of its core at a grid intersection within 60 feet. All creatures within 10 feet of this intersection take 2d6 fire damage and gain the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.aAQ6SW6iK0EVq8Ce]{Staggered} condition as the spray of molten stone and metal hardens. A target can attempt a DC 14 Reflex save to halve the damage and negate the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.aAQ6SW6iK0EVq8Ce]{Staggered} condition. Otherwise, the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.aAQ6SW6iK0EVq8Ce]{Staggered} condition lasts for 1 minute unless the target or an adjacent creature uses a full action to peel off enough rock and stone for the target to be able to move.</p>"
